1
00:00:10,176 --> 00:00:12,887
<i>Kenapa anda tiada teman lelaki?</i>

2
00:00:13,388 --> 00:00:14,764
<i>Saya selesa sendirian.</i>

3
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:17,600
<i>Apakah cabaran yang dihadapi</i>
<i>semasa bercinta?</i>

4
00:00:17,684 --> 00:00:19,060
<i>Tiada masa untuk diri sendiri.</i>

5
00:00:19,144 --> 00:00:21,521
<i>- Ciri-ciri fizikal…</i>
<i>- Kening tebal.</i>

6
00:00:23,773 --> 00:00:26,443
<i>Memulakan penjanaan AI yang diperibadikan.</i>

7
00:00:29,279 --> 00:00:31,281
<i>Pengoptimuman selesai.</i>

8
00:01:24,459 --> 00:01:29,047
<i>Tahniah kerana bertemu Gu Yeong-il,</i>
<i>teman lelaki yang dicipta khas untuk anda!</i>

9
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:29,964
Gila apa?

10
00:01:31,841 --> 00:01:33,510
Pengurus!

11
00:01:34,969 --> 00:01:36,179
PELANGGAN: 1
KHAS UNTUKKU

12
00:01:36,262 --> 00:01:37,931
Dah periksa. Tiada masalah.

13
00:01:38,014 --> 00:01:38,973
Apa?

14
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,683
Biar betul.

15
00:01:43,061 --> 00:01:46,147
Saya pening nak jawab,
jadi mungkin data saya salah.

16
00:01:46,231 --> 00:01:50,068
Tapi muka dia cacat teruk, okey?

17
00:01:50,151 --> 00:01:52,362
Taklah, saya rasa dia kacak.

18
00:01:52,445 --> 00:01:54,531
Tak kisahlah. Buat balik.

19
00:01:55,907 --> 00:01:57,242
- Buat balik?
- Ya.

20
00:01:57,325 --> 00:02:01,162
Penat saya jawab 2,000 soalan,
tapi akhirnya kena tengok muka dia.

21
00:02:01,246 --> 00:02:02,831
Lelaki itu…

22
00:02:03,331 --> 00:02:04,833
Maksud saya, Gu Yeong-il…

23
00:02:07,252 --> 00:02:08,169
Tukar sajalah.

24
00:02:08,253 --> 00:02:11,089
Dia dicipta khas untuk awak.

25
00:02:11,172 --> 00:02:14,425
Kami masukkan semua ciri yang awak suka.

26
00:02:14,926 --> 00:02:17,011
Cuba dulu. Mesti awak ubah fikiran.

27
00:02:17,095 --> 00:02:18,972
Kita patut buat satu lagi.

28
00:02:19,055 --> 00:02:19,889
Tak boleh.

29
00:02:20,765 --> 00:02:24,435
Saya dah cakap, bukan?
Awak boleh buat nombor 901 sekali saja.

30
00:02:25,103 --> 00:02:28,606
Tapi ini kes lain. Muka dia…

31
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:31,025
Kenapa dengan muka dia?

32
00:02:31,109 --> 00:02:33,653
Macam jin mata satu?
Ada tiga lubang hidung?

33
00:02:33,736 --> 00:02:36,406
Bukan salah kami.
Itu rupa lelaki idaman awak.

34
00:02:36,489 --> 00:02:37,532
Apa?

35
00:02:37,615 --> 00:02:40,160
Taklah. Dia bukan lelaki idaman saya.

36
00:02:40,243 --> 00:02:41,244
Itu mustahil.

37
00:02:42,453 --> 00:02:45,540
Saya jawab soal selidik
dengan serius dan jujur.

38
00:02:45,623 --> 00:02:47,917
Kami pun ambil serius hal ini.

39
00:02:48,001 --> 00:02:50,920
Peraturannya muktamad.
Boleh buat sekali saja.

40
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:59,012
Mereka dah gilakah? Mereka tak siuman!

41
00:03:07,770 --> 00:03:10,356
<i>Talian sokongan ditutup pada waktu ini.</i>

42
00:03:11,107 --> 00:03:12,609
Tak guna!

43
00:03:12,692 --> 00:03:14,944
Dalam ramai-ramai manusia,

44
00:03:16,029 --> 00:03:17,363
kenapa dia…

45
00:03:18,907 --> 00:03:19,908
Tak bolehlah.

46
00:03:19,991 --> 00:03:20,992
Saya suka awak.

47
00:03:21,075 --> 00:03:24,078
- Saya dah ada teman lelaki.
- Okey.

48
00:03:25,788 --> 00:03:28,082
Kenapalah dapat muka dia?

49
00:03:28,166 --> 00:03:30,793
EPISOD 6
LELAKI HIBRID

50
00:03:45,308 --> 00:03:46,142
Helo.

51
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,394
Hai.

52
00:03:51,814 --> 00:03:53,399
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

53
00:04:17,423 --> 00:04:19,092
<i>Pintu dibuka.</i>

54
00:04:23,596 --> 00:04:24,681
Tak nak keluar?

55
00:04:32,981 --> 00:04:35,608
Saya tahu awak pentingkan keunikan,

56
00:04:36,192 --> 00:04:38,152
tapi saya kurang gemar karya ini.

57
00:04:39,028 --> 00:04:42,282
Ia tak sempurna,
tapi temanya jelas dan visualnya bagus.

58
00:04:45,493 --> 00:04:47,495
Mungkin artisnya pelajar seni.

59
00:04:48,204 --> 00:04:52,292
Kalau kita baiki komposisi panelnya,
ia boleh jadi jauh lebih baik.

60
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:55,545
Jadi, awak rasa
kita patut utamakan potensi…

61
00:04:55,628 --> 00:04:58,631
<i>Park Kyeong-nam</i>
<i>sama macam lelaki idaman aku?</i>

62
00:04:58,715 --> 00:05:01,718
Itu tujuan pertandingan ini.
Nanti kita juga untung.

63
00:05:01,801 --> 00:05:03,803
<i>Tak mungkinlah.</i>

64
00:05:03,886 --> 00:05:06,639
Kelebihan dan kekurangannya jelas,
jadi mudah…

65
00:05:06,723 --> 00:05:07,932
<i>Eh, sekejap.</i>

66
00:05:08,683 --> 00:05:11,227
<i>Aku baru perasan kelopak matanya berlapis.</i>

67
00:05:12,061 --> 00:05:13,438
<i>Itulah yang aku suka.</i>

68
00:05:14,397 --> 00:05:17,317
<i>Hidungnya pun mancung…</i>

69
00:05:17,859 --> 00:05:20,028
<i>Bibir dia pula…</i>

70
00:05:31,873 --> 00:05:33,791
<i>Sudahlah, perempuan gila.</i>

71
00:05:37,962 --> 00:05:39,213
Awak tak setuju?

72
00:05:39,297 --> 00:05:40,214
Apa?

73
00:05:41,883 --> 00:05:43,593
Saya setuju.

74
00:05:44,969 --> 00:05:46,179
Yang ini bagus.

75
00:05:58,024 --> 00:05:59,359
Awak kenapa dari tadi?

76
00:06:01,903 --> 00:06:02,904
Kenapa?

77
00:06:02,987 --> 00:06:05,114
Awak cemas kalau saya perasan
awak tengok saya.

78
00:06:05,198 --> 00:06:08,451
Mana ada…

79
00:06:08,951 --> 00:06:11,371
Cuma muka awak…

80
00:06:11,454 --> 00:06:12,497
Kenapa?

81
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:14,749
Muka awak macam…

82
00:06:18,127 --> 00:06:19,212
Bukan muka awam.

83
00:06:19,796 --> 00:06:20,630
Apa?

84
00:06:20,713 --> 00:06:25,426
Bukan macam muka orang
yang kita boleh nampak merata-rata.

85
00:06:26,844 --> 00:06:27,929
Saya tak faham.

86
00:06:28,012 --> 00:06:29,931
Makanan sampai!

87
00:06:30,431 --> 00:06:31,766
Makanan sampai!

88
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:33,434
Jom makan dulu.

89
00:06:34,811 --> 00:06:35,812
Tak sabarnya!

90
00:06:46,447 --> 00:06:49,784
<i>Mustahil. Jangan harap.</i>

91
00:06:54,997 --> 00:06:56,165
Awak tak nak makan?

92
00:06:57,875 --> 00:06:58,876
Terima kasih.

93
00:07:06,634 --> 00:07:08,136
<i>Memang taklah.</i>

94
00:07:12,807 --> 00:07:14,058
Itu air saya.

95
00:07:18,896 --> 00:07:21,107
Maaf, ya.

96
00:07:27,071 --> 00:07:29,449
Dunia ini nak kenakan akukah?

97
00:07:33,536 --> 00:07:34,537
Tak guna!

98
00:07:48,134 --> 00:07:49,677
Ini pun saya nak.

99
00:07:51,387 --> 00:07:54,015
Di kedai buku pun
awak masih belanja sakan?

100
00:07:54,098 --> 00:07:56,601
Dah tak boleh beli baju, buku pun jadilah.

101
00:07:56,684 --> 00:07:58,436
Saya beli barang untuk janji temu.

102
00:07:58,519 --> 00:08:01,022
Bil kad kredit saya melambung.
Sewa rumah tak terbayar.

103
00:08:01,105 --> 00:08:02,773
Janji temu? Cepatnya?

104
00:08:03,357 --> 00:08:05,526
Cepat? Dah lama saya hidup solo.

105
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:06,694
Belum dua minggu.

106
00:08:07,987 --> 00:08:10,531
Betul. Saya patut aktif semula.

107
00:08:10,615 --> 00:08:12,575
Saya ada dua janji temu esok.

108
00:08:13,284 --> 00:08:15,036
Saya ada idea.

109
00:08:15,119 --> 00:08:18,664
Apa kata awak carikan calon untuk saya?

110
00:08:18,748 --> 00:08:20,625
Awak nak jumpa dua orang esok.

111
00:08:20,708 --> 00:08:24,420
Hei, orang sekarang boleh baca
banyak buku serentak.

112
00:08:24,504 --> 00:08:27,006
Mana ada orang keluar dengan seorang saja?

113
00:08:29,091 --> 00:08:30,927
Kim…

114
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,094
Kim Yeong-hun.

115
00:08:32,178 --> 00:08:34,597
Dia ada teman wanita? Sejak bila?

116
00:08:35,723 --> 00:08:38,309
Ada sesiapa dari Naemo?

117
00:08:39,060 --> 00:08:39,977
Park Kyeong…

118
00:08:40,061 --> 00:08:41,812
Apa? Dah sampai Park?

119
00:08:41,896 --> 00:08:46,275
Seo Hyeon-uk pun ada teman wanita dan…

120
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:47,527
Jeong-sik!

121
00:08:47,610 --> 00:08:48,694
Dia ada anak?

122
00:08:48,778 --> 00:08:50,071
Dah masuk sekolah.

123
00:08:50,154 --> 00:08:51,155
Comel.

124
00:08:53,282 --> 00:08:54,659
Apa? Itu saja?

125
00:08:55,618 --> 00:08:56,869
Seorang pun tak ada?

126
00:08:57,995 --> 00:08:59,914
Saya dah agak.

127
00:08:59,997 --> 00:09:03,084
Hei. Orang bujang dah tak wujudkah?

128
00:09:04,126 --> 00:09:06,796
Kenapa terkejut?
Awak tak nak bercinta pun.

129
00:09:07,922 --> 00:09:10,091
Keadaan dah lama teruk begini.

130
00:09:12,927 --> 00:09:15,137
<i>Jadi, semua lelaki baik dah berpunya,</i>

131
00:09:16,847 --> 00:09:18,891
<i>walaupun aku nak bercinta?</i>

132
00:09:26,566 --> 00:09:28,484
<i>Musim perayaan kali ini berbeza.</i>

133
00:09:34,657 --> 00:09:36,325
<i>Kali ini anda akan ditemani…</i>

134
00:09:41,330 --> 00:09:43,916
<i>Boyfriend on Demand di sisi anda</i>.

135
00:09:58,931 --> 00:10:01,350
<i>Baiklah. Aku layankan saja.</i>

136
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:03,436
<i>Sekali ini saja.</i>

137
00:10:32,131 --> 00:10:33,382
Enjinnya rosak terus.

138
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,760
Apa?

139
00:10:35,843 --> 00:10:38,763
Saya ikut sebab nampak asap.
Awak nak ke mana?

140
00:10:39,472 --> 00:10:40,890
Saya…

141
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:44,018
Saya tak tahu.

142
00:10:44,602 --> 00:10:46,979
Saya ikut saja jalan ini.

143
00:10:48,689 --> 00:10:49,940
Awak pelancong?

144
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:51,984
Pelancong?

145
00:11:08,042 --> 00:11:09,585
Kalau nak ikut, marilah.

146
00:11:10,878 --> 00:11:14,465
"Pertemuan pertama paling romantik
yang anda impikan?"

147
00:11:14,548 --> 00:11:18,052
Pergi bercuti dan jumpa lelaki
yang berjiwa bebas

148
00:11:18,135 --> 00:11:20,971
di tempat asing, macam dalam filem.

149
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,141
Waktu malam di sini bahaya.

150
00:11:26,602 --> 00:11:28,312
Awak nak saya naik motor?

151
00:11:28,396 --> 00:11:30,064
Habis, awak nak tunggu sini?

152
00:11:30,564 --> 00:11:32,775
Tak apalah. Saya takut.

153
00:11:47,289 --> 00:11:49,875
<i>Tahu-tahu saja, aku dah bonceng motor.</i>

154
00:12:05,474 --> 00:12:06,475
<i>Pelik rasanya.</i>

155
00:12:07,351 --> 00:12:11,856
<i>Aku duduk di belakang orang asing</i>
<i>yang mirip Park Kyeong-nam</i>

156
00:12:11,939 --> 00:12:15,359
<i>tanpa tahu pun arah tujuan kami,</i>
<i>jadi kenapa…</i>

157
00:12:17,528 --> 00:12:20,865
<i>Kenapa belakangnya selesa,</i>
<i>macam dicipta khas untuk aku?</i>

158
00:12:31,917 --> 00:12:33,586
<i>Angin yang bertiup pun…</i>

159
00:12:40,634 --> 00:12:42,470
<i>Begitu nyaman sekali.</i>

160
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:46,515
<i>Baunya pun…</i>

161
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:55,858
<i>Wangi.</i>

162
00:13:03,908 --> 00:13:05,242
<i>Apa yang aku rasa ini?</i>

163
00:13:21,133 --> 00:13:22,510
- Masuklah.
- Yeong-il.

164
00:13:24,929 --> 00:13:25,930
Hei.

165
00:13:26,931 --> 00:13:28,933
- Sean.
- Hei. Apa khabar?

166
00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:30,351
Awak okey?

167
00:13:30,434 --> 00:13:32,645
- Awak minum banyak semalam.
- Itulah!

168
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:36,315
Hai.

169
00:13:38,776 --> 00:13:41,946
<i>Kenapa semuanya terperinci?</i>
<i>Nampak realistik betul.</i>

170
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:54,625
Oh mak kau.

171
00:13:55,209 --> 00:13:56,877
<i>Pelayan bar. Kawan Yeong-il.</i>

172
00:13:56,961 --> 00:13:59,922
Orang selalu takut nampak saya.
Tapi saya baik.

173
00:14:00,506 --> 00:14:02,007
Saya pernah nampak awak.

174
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:04,718
Saya cuma terkejut tadi!

175
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:09,223
Saya nak macam biasa dan dia punya pula…

176
00:14:09,306 --> 00:14:11,475
Sekejap. Biar saya teka.

177
00:14:17,648 --> 00:14:18,649
Okey!

178
00:14:36,375 --> 00:14:38,043
- Wah.
- Awak suka?

179
00:14:39,211 --> 00:14:41,380
- Suka sangat.
- Dah habis, cakap.

180
00:14:44,216 --> 00:14:45,634
Ada apa datang seorang diri?

181
00:14:46,468 --> 00:14:49,388
Saya nak betulkan balik hidup saya.

182
00:14:51,515 --> 00:14:54,184
Sebenarnya, saya baru putus cinta.

183
00:14:55,603 --> 00:14:56,437
Kenapa?

184
00:14:57,521 --> 00:14:58,480
Dia curang.

185
00:14:59,523 --> 00:15:00,649
Dia main kayu tiga?

186
00:15:01,901 --> 00:15:02,735
Kayu 10,000.

187
00:15:07,031 --> 00:15:08,032
Apa?

188
00:15:09,491 --> 00:15:10,743
Sepuluh ribu wanita.

189
00:15:19,126 --> 00:15:23,422
Ini ruang makan.
Buatlah kopi di sana kalau nak.

190
00:15:24,673 --> 00:15:25,674
Terima kasih.

191
00:15:26,759 --> 00:15:30,512
Tidurlah di bilik itu.
Nanti saya beritahu pemilik hostel.

192
00:15:31,096 --> 00:15:31,972
Nah.

193
00:15:35,851 --> 00:15:37,353
Saya gembira jumpa awak.

194
00:15:54,203 --> 00:15:55,579
Su-ji?

195
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,915
Hei, Su-ji!

196
00:15:57,998 --> 00:16:00,668
Lama tak jumpa!
Nasib baik awak hidup lagi!

197
00:16:02,252 --> 00:16:03,587
Kasarnya bahasa.

198
00:16:05,798 --> 00:16:07,007
Awak kenal saya?

199
00:16:07,091 --> 00:16:08,884
<i>Yu-ra, pelancong Korea.</i>

200
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:12,888
Dulu kita kenal.

201
00:16:12,972 --> 00:16:15,432
Sebenarnya, tak. Saya tak kenal awak.

202
00:16:15,516 --> 00:16:18,644
Nampaknya, orang pelik
yang baru dah datang.

203
00:16:23,023 --> 00:16:25,275
Tolong jangan tutup pintu.

204
00:16:25,776 --> 00:16:28,320
Pintu itu rosak.

205
00:16:28,821 --> 00:16:30,155
Sekali awak tutup,

206
00:16:31,532 --> 00:16:33,117
ia tak boleh dibuka.

207
00:16:34,076 --> 00:16:35,619
Saya tak tahu. Maaf, kak.

208
00:16:37,538 --> 00:16:38,956
Jangan kakakkan saya.

209
00:16:39,456 --> 00:16:40,457
Encik!

210
00:16:41,375 --> 00:16:43,252
Siapa bawa perempuan ini?

211
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:47,965
Aku paling suka dia jadi Su-ji.

212
00:16:48,924 --> 00:16:50,718
Cik Choi pun tak segarang ini.

213
00:17:05,357 --> 00:17:07,359
Tak sangka dia bawa saya ke hostelnya.

214
00:17:09,778 --> 00:17:10,612
Alamak.

215
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,450
Dia takkan masuk sini, bukan?

216
00:17:18,203 --> 00:17:19,872
Awak tak nak makan?

217
00:17:21,415 --> 00:17:22,499
Nanti saya datang!

218
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:33,343
Teruknya!

219
00:17:34,219 --> 00:17:36,555
Tawar nak mampus.

220
00:17:38,515 --> 00:17:40,225
Saya tak boleh habiskan.

221
00:17:46,106 --> 00:17:47,733
Teman sebilik awak cerewet?

222
00:17:48,358 --> 00:17:49,443
Ya.

223
00:17:50,319 --> 00:17:52,404
Kereta awak siap pagi lusa.

224
00:17:53,072 --> 00:17:54,448
Okey. Terima kasih.

225
00:17:57,493 --> 00:18:00,662
Boleh saya tanya, awak kerja sebagai apa?

226
00:18:02,581 --> 00:18:03,415
Saya melukis.

227
00:18:03,499 --> 00:18:04,500
Apa?

228
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:05,959
Melukis?

229
00:18:08,003 --> 00:18:09,171
Jadi, awak artis?

230
00:18:10,422 --> 00:18:12,508
Saya mengembara dan lukis
apa yang saya suka.

231
00:18:13,592 --> 00:18:14,635
<i>Mi-rae.</i>

232
00:18:14,718 --> 00:18:17,054
Giliran awak. Apa ciri lelaki idaman awak?

233
00:18:17,137 --> 00:18:18,305
Lelaki idaman saya?

234
00:18:18,388 --> 00:18:20,891
Saya pilih Gang Dong-won. Dia, Ju Ji-hoon.

235
00:18:24,186 --> 00:18:25,020
Saya suka

236
00:18:25,896 --> 00:18:27,231
lelaki hibrid.

237
00:18:28,482 --> 00:18:30,609
- Maksudnya?
- Tengoklah.

238
