471
00:33:52,697 --> 00:33:56,451
Awak suka lelaki yang relaks.
Dia nampak skema.

472
00:33:57,452 --> 00:33:58,286
Betulkah?

473
00:33:59,704 --> 00:34:00,538
Betul, bukan?

474
00:34:01,205 --> 00:34:03,791
Ya, itulah maksud saya.

475
00:34:04,375 --> 00:34:05,460
Minum!

476
00:34:06,461 --> 00:34:07,295
Minum.

477
00:34:12,216 --> 00:34:13,301
<i>Aku dah agak.</i>

478
00:34:14,302 --> 00:34:15,511
<i>Bukan dia orangnya.</i>

479
00:34:24,896 --> 00:34:26,981
PESTA KOMIK BUSAN KE-27

480
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:50,505
Awak dah tiba.

481
00:34:51,422 --> 00:34:52,381
Ya.

482
00:34:56,052 --> 00:34:56,886
Sekejap…

483
00:34:58,805 --> 00:34:59,639
Rambut awak…

484
00:35:03,059 --> 00:35:06,062
Ia melekat semasa saya beli
bunga Cik Yun agaknya.

485
00:35:07,605 --> 00:35:09,023
Tahniah.

486
00:35:09,524 --> 00:35:13,319
Dia mungkin tak menang,
tapi saya beli dulu. Manalah tahu.

487
00:35:13,402 --> 00:35:17,115
Saya harap ada berita baik
untuk Hwany juga.

488
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:19,826
Harapnya begitulah.

489
00:35:24,872 --> 00:35:25,706
Oh, ya.

490
00:35:26,457 --> 00:35:27,291
Seo Mi-rae?

491
00:35:28,167 --> 00:35:30,169
Janganlah fikir sangat tentang

492
00:35:31,129 --> 00:35:32,547
kata-kata saya dulu.

493
00:35:36,467 --> 00:35:37,552
Saya okey.

494
00:35:42,390 --> 00:35:43,474
Jom masuk.

495
00:35:48,062 --> 00:35:52,984
Mari kita mulakan upacara anugerah
Pesta Komik Busan ke-27!

496
00:35:59,699 --> 00:36:03,411
Tiada penghormatan yang seindah
kasih sayang peminat.

497
00:36:03,494 --> 00:36:06,372
Oleh itu, anugerah ini sangat bermakna.

498
00:36:06,956 --> 00:36:11,377
Dengan undian luar biasa para peminat,
Anugerah Populariti jatuh kepada…

499
00:36:12,378 --> 00:36:13,254
Tahniah.

500
00:36:13,337 --> 00:36:16,048
Yun Song, penulis <i>Dia yang Perlu Dikenal</i>.

501
00:36:16,132 --> 00:36:17,300
Tahniah!

502
00:36:20,428 --> 00:36:22,013
- Tahniah!
- Terima kasih.

503
00:36:22,096 --> 00:36:24,640
…percintaan pewaris harta
dan pekerja hotel.

504
00:36:24,724 --> 00:36:27,226
Dengan watak yang menawan
dan plot menarik,

505
00:36:27,310 --> 00:36:28,811
ia mendapat sambutan…

506
00:36:28,895 --> 00:36:30,062
Tahniah.

507
00:36:30,146 --> 00:36:31,147
Tahniah!

508
00:36:35,234 --> 00:36:36,068
Okey.

509
00:36:36,152 --> 00:36:38,654
Dah banyak kali juga

510
00:36:38,738 --> 00:36:41,866
kamu beri saya Anugerah Populariti saja.

511
00:36:44,535 --> 00:36:48,706
Saya patut berterima kasih.
Setidaknya, dapat juga anugerah.

512
00:36:50,583 --> 00:36:53,961
Tapi kalau saya dapat lagi
anugerah ini tahun depan,

513
00:36:54,045 --> 00:36:55,963
saya nak boikot acara kamu.

514
00:37:03,304 --> 00:37:05,723
Saya gurau sajalah. Aduhai!

515
00:37:06,349 --> 00:37:07,433
Okey.

516
00:37:07,516 --> 00:37:08,351
Terima kasih.

517
00:37:14,232 --> 00:37:18,653
Seterusnya, atas kejayaan membawa
nafas baru kepada industri komik,

518
00:37:18,736 --> 00:37:20,655
pemenang Anugerah Artis Baru…

519
00:37:21,155 --> 00:37:22,990
Tahniah, Hwasubun.

520
00:37:23,699 --> 00:37:24,867
Tahniah.

521
00:37:26,577 --> 00:37:30,623
<i>Tak Okey</i>, kisah atlet pelajar yang jatuh
dalam kurungan bawah tanah di dunia lain,

522
00:37:30,706 --> 00:37:33,960
dipuji kerana perspektif nakal
dan ekspresi berani.

523
00:37:34,043 --> 00:37:35,586
Tahniah!

524
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,050
Kita teruskan.

525
00:37:41,133 --> 00:37:44,011
- Tak apa.
- Anugerah Komik Web Terbaik.

526
00:37:44,095 --> 00:37:48,683
Siapakah yang berjaya mengatasi persaingan
untuk meraih penghormatan ini?

527
00:37:49,267 --> 00:37:51,936
Saya akan umumkan
pemenang Komik Web Terbaik.

528
00:37:52,019 --> 00:37:56,524
Pemenang Komik Web Terbaik
Pesta Komik Busan ke-27 ialah…

529
00:37:58,859 --> 00:38:01,862
<i>PlanC </i>oleh Hwany. Tahniah!

530
00:38:04,949 --> 00:38:05,866
Syabas!

531
00:38:06,826 --> 00:38:07,660
Saya menang?

532
00:38:08,286 --> 00:38:10,913
<i>PlanC </i>ialah komedi gelap tentang anak muda

533
00:38:10,997 --> 00:38:14,709
yang mencari hidup baru di desa,
tapi terjebak dalam insiden misteri.

534
00:38:14,792 --> 00:38:18,879
Dengan garapan kemas,
tema yang jelas dan plot bermutu,

535
00:38:18,963 --> 00:38:21,382
ia menawan hati pembaca dan pengkritik.

536
00:38:21,465 --> 00:38:22,300
Syabas.

537
00:38:22,383 --> 00:38:24,927
Tahniah atas kemenangan ini!

538
00:38:26,512 --> 00:38:27,513
Terima kasih.

539
00:38:30,057 --> 00:38:34,562
Saya tak sangka dapat
anugerah utama seperti ini, jadi…

540
00:38:34,645 --> 00:38:35,938
Kacaknya awak!

541
00:38:36,022 --> 00:38:36,856
Terima kasih.

542
00:38:36,939 --> 00:38:38,691
Itu pun kau kata kacak?

543
00:38:38,774 --> 00:38:40,609
Saya tak tahu nak kata apa.

544
00:38:40,693 --> 00:38:41,944
Jangan menangis!

545
00:38:42,028 --> 00:38:44,864
Buat Kyeong-nam
yang banyak membantu dari awal,

546
00:38:44,947 --> 00:38:46,866
Pengarah Hwang Byeong-hak,

547
00:38:46,949 --> 00:38:49,618
Penerbit Cho Min-seok,
editor saya yang setia,

548
00:38:49,702 --> 00:38:50,828
dan semua yang…

549
00:38:50,911 --> 00:38:52,455
Saya rasa nak mengamuk.

550
00:38:52,538 --> 00:38:53,748
…terima kasih.

551
00:38:53,831 --> 00:38:56,083
Anugerah ini milik kita semua.

552
00:38:56,167 --> 00:38:57,084
Terima kasih!

553
00:38:57,168 --> 00:38:58,753
Awak layak menang!

554
00:39:04,467 --> 00:39:05,551
Lepaslah!

555
00:39:05,634 --> 00:39:08,012
Kenapa datang jauh-jauh,
tapi buat perangai?

556
00:39:08,095 --> 00:39:09,597
Hei, saya kata jangan!

557
00:39:10,181 --> 00:39:11,474
Teruk betullah.

558
00:39:11,557 --> 00:39:14,935
Hei, saya datang bukan
untuk jadi pengiring saja.

559
00:39:15,019 --> 00:39:16,896
Terima kasih! Ya.

560
00:39:18,647 --> 00:39:20,316
Kenapa awak cakap begitu?

561
00:39:20,399 --> 00:39:24,904
Kamu kerja bawah satu bumbung.
Kenapa tak ucap tahniah kepada dia?

562
00:39:24,987 --> 00:39:28,240
Bila awak nak matang?

563
00:39:29,492 --> 00:39:31,077
Dulu awak tanya saya

564
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:35,164
kalau saya nak biarkan komik budak itu
menyelit pada hari komik saya.

565
00:39:36,290 --> 00:39:37,666
Sudahlah, mari masuk.

566
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:38,918
- Lepas.
- Marilah!

567
00:39:39,001 --> 00:39:40,669
Lepaskan saya. Saya serius!

568
00:39:41,337 --> 00:39:42,588
Seo Mi-rae!

569
00:40:05,611 --> 00:40:06,529
Awak okey?

570
00:40:09,156 --> 00:40:10,950
Ya. Saya okey.

571
00:40:12,618 --> 00:40:13,452
Cik Yun.

572
00:40:14,328 --> 00:40:16,247
Kenapa duduk di luar? Masuklah.

573
00:40:17,665 --> 00:40:20,376
Menyampah betullah aku.

574
00:40:31,095 --> 00:40:33,264
Semuanya jasa kamu. Terima kasih!

575
00:40:36,350 --> 00:40:39,270
- Sedapnya minum malam ini.
- Tahniah!

576
00:40:39,353 --> 00:40:41,105
Apa? Terima kasih, semua!

577
00:40:42,189 --> 00:40:43,983
Bunga? Awak ambillah.

578
00:40:47,486 --> 00:40:48,654
Jom ambil gambar.

579
00:40:48,737 --> 00:40:49,738
- Boleh!
- Bagus.

580
00:40:49,822 --> 00:40:51,907
Okey. Satu, dua…

581
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:55,453
- Minum!
- Tahniah.

582
00:40:55,995 --> 00:40:57,538
Tahniah!

583
00:41:04,378 --> 00:41:06,964
Dulu awak kata tak boleh makan mentah.

584
00:41:09,508 --> 00:41:11,427
Saya nak cuba makan hari ini.

585
00:41:11,510 --> 00:41:12,344
Yakah?

586
00:41:13,095 --> 00:41:13,929
Cik Yun.

587
00:41:14,013 --> 00:41:16,932
Saya nak belanja hari ini.
Jom pesan wiski.

588
00:41:17,016 --> 00:41:18,767
- Wah!
- Awak memang hebat!

589
00:41:19,685 --> 00:41:21,187
Yang betul-betul mahal?

590
00:41:21,270 --> 00:41:22,188
Mestilah!

591
00:41:22,271 --> 00:41:23,189
Okey!

592
00:41:24,982 --> 00:41:26,567
Saya nak jawab sekejap.

593
00:41:28,694 --> 00:41:29,528
Helo?

594
00:41:30,112 --> 00:41:33,282
Apa? Macam mana awak tahu
nak telefon saya?

595
00:41:33,365 --> 00:41:35,451
Kami sedang raikannya.

596
00:41:35,534 --> 00:41:38,120
Terima kasih. Saya tak layak dipuji.

597
00:41:38,204 --> 00:41:39,955
Nanti kita makan di Seoul.

598
00:41:40,039 --> 00:41:41,916
Ya, En. Cho. Selamat malam.

599
00:41:42,875 --> 00:41:43,709
En. Cho?

600
00:41:44,335 --> 00:41:46,170
Penerbit Cho telefon awak?

601
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:47,546
Hulur telefon.

602
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:49,590
Kenapa? Apa halnya?

603
00:41:49,673 --> 00:41:51,383
Tak guna.

604
00:41:52,384 --> 00:41:54,011
Saya tak percaya betul.

605
00:41:55,095 --> 00:41:56,514
<i>Nombor yang anda dail…</i>

606
00:41:56,597 --> 00:42:00,017
Kalau saya telefon dia,
kenapa terus masuk mel suara?

607
00:42:00,601 --> 00:42:01,852
Dia sibuk agaknya.

608
00:42:02,853 --> 00:42:04,522
Cik Yun, relakslah.

609
00:42:04,605 --> 00:42:05,523
Hei.

610
00:42:05,606 --> 00:42:10,444
Kenapa dia cakap baik-baik dengan awak,
tapi berbulan tak layan panggilan saya?

611
00:42:10,528 --> 00:42:12,029
Manalah saya tahu?

612
00:42:12,112 --> 00:42:14,240
Kenapa dia sekat nombor saya,
tapi telefon awak?

613
00:42:14,323 --> 00:42:16,575
Sebab awak menyusahkan orang!

614
00:42:20,079 --> 00:42:20,913
Apa?

615
00:42:20,996 --> 00:42:23,082
Bukan itu yang saya…

616
00:42:23,165 --> 00:42:25,334
- Cik Yun.
- Berani betul dia.

617
00:42:25,417 --> 00:42:27,753
Saya dah hilang sabar dengan awak.

618
00:42:27,836 --> 00:42:32,675
Awak berpakat dengan Cho
untuk kenakan saya, bukan?

619
00:42:32,758 --> 00:42:35,386
Saya dengar dia bising
kepada Pengarah Hwang

620
00:42:35,469 --> 00:42:37,596
sebab dia pilih kasih antara kita.

621
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:41,100
Awak tukar tarikh siaran komik awak
untuk sabotaj saya, ya?

622
00:42:41,183 --> 00:42:43,269
Itu tak ada kaitan langsung.

623
00:42:43,352 --> 00:42:45,145
Itu tak benar, Cik Yun.

624
00:42:45,229 --> 00:42:48,315
En. Hwang yang tentukan tarikh siaran.

625
00:42:49,441 --> 00:42:51,944
Kelakar betullah. Jadi, awak…

626
00:42:54,029 --> 00:42:55,447
Tak, tunggu dulu.

627
00:42:55,531 --> 00:42:58,867
Saya sebenarnya tak nak ungkit hal ini.

628
00:42:59,618 --> 00:43:00,452
Apa?

629
00:43:01,870 --> 00:43:03,163
Awak belum lupakan saya?

630
00:43:08,711 --> 00:43:09,753
Apa?

631
00:43:11,088 --> 00:43:14,425
Semasa Cho sewakan studio
untuk kita di Hapjeong-dong,

632
00:43:14,508 --> 00:43:17,886
awak yang diam-diam
tinggalkan snek di depan bilik saya.

633
00:43:17,970 --> 00:43:21,599
Saya pernah nampak awak lari
selepas buat begitu.

634
00:43:22,558 --> 00:43:24,560
Janganlah begitu. Itu…

635
00:43:24,643 --> 00:43:27,229
Saya tak layan perasaan awak,

636
00:43:27,313 --> 00:43:30,316
tapi perlukah awak berdendam
dan sabotaj saya?

637
00:43:30,941 --> 00:43:32,359
Dengki betullah.

638
00:43:33,444 --> 00:43:34,653
- Mana ada.
- Apa?

639
00:43:34,737 --> 00:43:37,865
Cho beritahu awak
saya tak makan dan buang semuanya?

640
00:43:37,948 --> 00:43:39,450
Teruk betul.

641
00:43:39,950 --> 00:43:41,452
Itu…

642
00:43:42,786 --> 00:43:43,746
Sebenarnya…

643
00:43:43,829 --> 00:43:45,039
Apa?

644
00:43:46,290 --> 00:43:47,791
Itu untuk So-yeong!

645
00:43:51,670 --> 00:43:52,671
Siapa So-yeong?

646
00:43:56,175 --> 00:43:57,092
Pembantu awak?

647
00:44:01,847 --> 00:44:05,184
Cik Yun? Berhentilah tuang.

648
00:44:05,934 --> 00:44:07,144
Air dah tumpah.

649
00:44:09,438 --> 00:44:11,357
Saya nak ke tandas sekejap.

650
00:44:12,149 --> 00:44:13,108
Biar dia lalu.

651
00:44:17,655 --> 00:44:18,739
Apa dah jadi?

652
00:44:22,159 --> 00:44:25,663
Saya bukan jenis yang syok sendiri.

653
00:44:26,455 --> 00:44:30,376
Kalau tengok situasi kita dulu,
memanglah saya salah faham.

654
00:44:30,459 --> 00:44:33,128
Sesiapa pun akan fikir macam saya.

655
00:44:33,212 --> 00:44:35,214
- Betul.
- Memanglah.

656
00:44:37,633 --> 00:44:40,260
Saya bukan jenis perasan. Okey?

657
00:44:41,220 --> 00:44:42,554
Saya ada teman lelaki.

658
00:44:42,638 --> 00:44:44,473
Saya ada teman lelakilah!

659
00:44:44,556 --> 00:44:47,226
- Dia ada teman lelaki.
- Merepek betullah.

660
00:44:48,352 --> 00:44:50,479
- Manalah kita tahu.
- Apa kita nak buat?

661
00:44:50,562 --> 00:44:52,189
<i>Aduh, tolonglah…</i>

662
00:44:59,279 --> 00:45:01,323
Sikit saja lagi. Dah nak sampai.

663
00:45:02,282 --> 00:45:03,492
Aduhai!

664
00:45:10,791 --> 00:45:12,459
Awak memang nak saya mati.

665
00:45:21,927 --> 00:45:22,845
JJONG

666
00:45:26,724 --> 00:45:28,976
Ya? Saya tolong jawab telefon Cik Yun.

667
00:45:29,059 --> 00:45:31,895
<i>Ada apa-apa jadi kepada Song?</i>

668
00:45:33,147 --> 00:45:36,066
Dia dapat anugerah dan mabuk selepas itu.

669
00:45:36,150 --> 00:45:37,901
<i>Tapi dia di tempat selamat?</i>

670
00:45:37,985 --> 00:45:40,988
Ya. Dia dah balik tidur di biliknya.

671
00:45:41,071 --> 00:45:43,991
<i>Awak tolong bawa dia balik? Terima kasih.</i>

672
00:45:44,074 --> 00:45:47,745
Sama-sama. Tapi ini siapa?

673
00:45:47,828 --> 00:45:49,496
<i>Saya tak kenalkan diri pun.</i>

674
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:52,332
<i>Saya teman lelaki Song.</i>

675
00:45:53,500 --> 00:45:54,710
Apa?

676
00:45:54,793 --> 00:45:57,171
<i>Saya bercinta dengan Song.</i>

677
00:45:57,254 --> 00:45:58,088
Wah.

678
00:45:59,757 --> 00:46:02,342
Maaf, saya tak sangka
awak teman lelaki dia.

679
00:46:02,426 --> 00:46:05,763
<i>Kami dah lama bercinta.</i>
<i>Dia belum beritahu orang agaknya.</i>

680
00:46:05,846 --> 00:46:08,098
<i>Apa pun, terima kasihlah tolong dia.</i>

681
00:46:08,682 --> 00:46:10,934
Sama-sama. Selamat malam.

682
00:46:22,446 --> 00:46:25,365
Jadi, betullah dia ada teman lelaki?

683
00:46:27,951 --> 00:46:30,454
<i>Dah hantar dia? Awak datang balik tak?</i>

684
00:46:30,537 --> 00:46:32,372
<i>Kami nak sambung parti!</i>

685
00:46:32,873 --> 00:46:34,416
<i>Saya datang sekarang.</i>

686
00:46:37,419 --> 00:46:38,754
Park Kyeong-nam.

687
00:46:38,837 --> 00:46:42,007
Dah lama awak rapat dengan Hwany?

688
00:46:43,634 --> 00:46:45,803
- Siapa kata kami rapat?
- Apa?

689
00:46:46,845 --> 00:46:48,180
Awak kelakarlah!

690
00:46:49,181 --> 00:46:51,433
Kami rapat.
Dia tak boleh hidup tanpa saya.

691
00:46:51,517 --> 00:46:53,185
Janganlah mengarut.

692
00:47:16,875 --> 00:47:17,709
JI-YEON

693
00:47:17,793 --> 00:47:21,630
<i>Bosan tak kerja di Busan?</i>
<i>Nak dengar cerita janji temu saya?</i>

694
00:47:23,006 --> 00:47:24,591
Dia tak faham-faham.

695
00:47:27,469 --> 00:47:29,179
Tak nak.

696
00:47:43,026 --> 00:47:46,154
Saya beri awak 10 saat. Cerita cepat.

697
00:47:47,531 --> 00:47:49,199
<i>Hei, 10 saat sekejap sangat.</i>

698
00:47:51,451 --> 00:47:52,286
Apa?

699
00:47:53,078 --> 00:47:54,121
Macam mana…

700
00:47:54,204 --> 00:47:57,291
<i>Kereta awak dah siap.</i>
<i>Saya nak bawa awak jalan-jalan.</i>

701
00:47:57,791 --> 00:47:58,792
<i>Awak di mana?</i>

702
00:48:00,460 --> 00:48:02,296
Saya tak boleh pergi sekarang.

703
00:48:02,379 --> 00:48:03,213
<i>Kenapa?</i>

704
00:48:04,798 --> 00:48:07,634
<i>Saya dengar ombak. Saya pun ada di pantai.</i>

705
00:48:07,718 --> 00:48:09,386
<i>Saya boleh ke sana.</i>

706
00:48:10,554 --> 00:48:12,723
Macam mana?

707
00:48:13,223 --> 00:48:15,183
<i>Awak ingat saya tak boleh datang?</i>

708
00:48:18,729 --> 00:48:20,564
Macam mana dia nak datang?

709
00:48:21,732 --> 00:48:23,150
Mengarut saja.

710
00:49:13,408 --> 00:49:14,868
Awak betul-betul datang?

711
00:49:27,714 --> 00:49:28,882
Panasnya.

712
00:49:44,064 --> 00:49:45,399
Awak buat apa di sini?

713
00:49:49,653 --> 00:49:50,487
<i>Helo?</i>

714
00:49:51,697 --> 00:49:52,781
<i>Helo?</i>

715
00:50:14,636 --> 00:50:16,430
Aduh! Sakitlah.

716
00:50:16,513 --> 00:50:21,476
Ibu saya nak saya jadi doktor
sejak saya kecil.

717
00:50:21,560 --> 00:50:23,895
Saya berjaya lulus bab bahagi,

718
00:50:23,979 --> 00:50:25,731
tapi tak pandai buat pecahan.

719
00:50:25,814 --> 00:50:27,983
Tahan sikit, ya? Okey, dah siap.

720
00:50:28,066 --> 00:50:30,736
Tak apa, ini mimpi saja.

721
00:50:31,737 --> 00:50:32,821
Hei, awak!

722
00:50:38,201 --> 00:50:40,328
Siapa lelaki kacak ini?

723
00:50:40,412 --> 00:50:41,621
Hebat.

724
00:50:41,705 --> 00:50:43,540
Boleh awak fokus?

725
00:50:43,623 --> 00:50:45,459
Peliknya mimpi ini.

726
00:50:46,460 --> 00:50:48,378
- Apa?
- Ini mesti mimpi.

727
00:50:48,462 --> 00:50:50,130
- Ini mimpi, bukan?
- Apa?

728
00:50:53,341 --> 00:50:54,968
- Tapi kenapa sakit?
- Tepi.

729
00:51:14,404 --> 00:51:15,655
Ini siapa pula?

730
00:51:16,656 --> 00:51:19,576
Serahkan kertas di dalam laci
kalau awak sayang nyawa.

731
00:51:19,659 --> 00:51:21,661
Okey. Yalah.

732
00:51:21,745 --> 00:51:23,497
Saya dah faham.

733
00:51:24,081 --> 00:51:25,749
Baguslah awak cepat faham.

734
00:51:33,965 --> 00:51:36,635
Peliknya. Mana penyelamat saya?

735
00:51:36,718 --> 00:51:38,136
- Lepaskan saya!
- Helo?

736
00:51:38,220 --> 00:51:39,638
Mana teman lelaki saya?

737
00:51:46,436 --> 00:51:47,771
Cik puan!

738
00:51:47,854 --> 00:51:49,439
Cik puan!

739
00:51:49,523 --> 00:51:50,649
Penjahat durjana!

740
00:51:53,276 --> 00:51:54,111
Dolsoe?

741
00:51:54,736 --> 00:51:56,822
Cik puan! Keparat!

742
00:51:57,322 --> 00:51:58,865
- Dolsoe!
- Apa…

743
00:51:59,449 --> 00:52:00,534
Ya!

744
00:53:13,023 --> 00:53:14,733
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

